Time":"2018-01-28T21:45:39.000Z","msg":"sor sor sor <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日冇 network post 唔到圖<br />\n而家補返<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/045227_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F045227_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2912edbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日其實都冇咩plan 起身一陣 就去左個水族館 9 行 <br />\n由住果到去水族館 要坐metro 加上今日可能會去其他地方9行 所以買張day pass 會抵屌啲(好似係)  <br />\n<br />\n因為今日星期日 水族館好撚多人 都要排一陣隊先買到ticket <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/050220_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F050220_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fdf9e5be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個水族館真係冇咩特別 可能小妹on9 因為我覺得隻隻魚都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海洋公園會仲好睇 好似係<br />\n魚1號<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/051013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F051013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82840cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魚2號<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/051221_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F051221_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3fc64d7d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果看著我不妨濛一點 我影果時條魚同我咁講<br />\n<br />\n魚 3 4 5 6 7號<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/051435_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F051435_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c15ab7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為太多魚 不能盡錄 但同係街市個啲差唔多<br />\n<br />\n唯一特別係水族館 係有陸上動物 如 青蛙 蟲 蛇 有毛嘅老鼠 食肉嘅蜥蜴 on9嘅人類等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nbtw 去到水族館呢一part 好似叫熱帶咩咩<br />\n一入到去就有回家的感覺 啲濕氣高撚到一個點 十足十香港summer 想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/052152_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F052152_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ba8d3b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多陣就去左 Lake Geneve 正正子終於睇到雪山 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/053410_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F053410_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f2a31630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後一直去東邊9行 睇左一個我覺得最靚嘅日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 記得唔好太遠 因為回程要自己行返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/053311_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F053311_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=14be4031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/053324_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F053324_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d22e15e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有時間 可以去埋呢個博物館<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呢就冇時間 如果有巴打去過就同我講聲有咩睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/054307_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F054307_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7ebd04f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日再update <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}